skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: tourist guide
des:
In this skill, we have provided the information that the tourist needs when going on a trip in Jordan and Dubai, an example of the best tourist areas in Jordan and Dubai, hotel and restaurant services, weather conditions, etc.

Invocation Name: tourist guide
To start, just say "Alexa, launch tourist guide " or "Alexa, open tourist guide" to get started".
At any time, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop".
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
